Version 0.1.13 (dan)
	* Fix potential crasher when an empty string (instead of nil) was passed.
	* Update graph x-axis time auto-magic.
	* Don't bother with y-label on percent graphs.

Version 0.1.12 (dan)
	* Don't require .cdb for filename.
	* Raise Errno::* SystemCallErrors for errno failures.

Version 0.1.11 (dan)
	* Fix graph y format - go back to array based gnuplot sets.

Version 0.1.10 (dan)
	* Meta methods for header setter and getter - missed from [PLATFORM-227]
	* Update to match CircularDB API - handle return values / exceptions better.

Version 0.1.9 (dan)
	* Add reset test.
	* Allow arbitrary graph sizes [PLATFORM-226]
	* Fix name issue [PLATFORM-227]
	* Fix nil causing an overflow to be recorded [PLATFORM-228]
	* Fix reset counters causing an overflow [PLATFORM-229]
	* Allow Ruby Time objects to be passed in directly. [PLATFORM-230]

